# Optional Orchestra server settings.
# Copy to .env and uncomment lines you need, or export them in your shell / launchd plist.
# None of these are required for a basic local install.
#
# Dual-instance workflow (recommended): use ./dev-start.sh and ./stable-update.sh
# instead of hand-editing .env. See docs/internal/dual-instance.md.

# Separate data dirs for dev vs stable (default when unset: ~/.agent-task-tracker)
# ORCHESTRA_DATA_DIR=$HOME/.orchestra/dev
# ORCHESTRA_DATA_DIR=$HOME/.orchestra/stable

# HTTP port (default: 47823; server picks the next free port if busy)
# PORT=47823

# Bind address (default in server: 127.0.0.1)
# HOST=127.0.0.1

# Pin hook/extension tokens instead of auto-generated files under ~/.agent-task-tracker/
# BROWSER_CHAT_TOKEN=
# CURSOR_HOOK_TOKEN=
# CODEX_HOOK_TOKEN=
# CLAUDE_HOOK_TOKEN=
# GEMINI_HOOK_TOKEN=
